html
  head
    meta(charset='UTF-8')
    meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0')
  body(
    style='margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #fdfaf9; font-family: Arial, sans-serif'
  )
  include header.pug

  table(
    width='100%',
    cellpadding='0',
    cellspacing='0',
    border='0',
    style='padding: 20px 0'
  )
    tr
      td(align='center')
        table(
          width='600',
          cellpadding='0',
          cellspacing='0',
          border='0',
          style='border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden'
        )
          tr
            td(style='padding: 20px 30px 0 30px')
              p(
                style='color: #333; font-size: 16px; margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-weight: bold'
              ) Hi #{ firstName || 'there' },
          tr
            td(style='padding: 20px 30px 0 30px')
              p(style='color: #333; font-size: 16px; margin: 0 0 16px 0') Welcome to Career Fingerprint. You're all set.
              p(style='color: #333; font-size: 16px; margin: 0 0 16px 0') The idea is simple: log what you accomplish each week, and Career Fingerprint turns it into something useful — a resume, talking points for your next review, or just a record you can look back on.
              p(style='color: #333; font-size: 16px; margin: 0 0 16px 0') Most people wait until they need a resume to think about this stuff. You'll have a head start.

          tr
            td(style='padding: 20px 30px 0 30px')
              p(
                style='color: #333; font-size: 14px; margin: 0 0 8px 0; font-weight: bold'
              ) A few things worth knowing:
              ul(
                style='color: #333; font-size: 16px; padding-left: 20px; margin: 0 0 16px 0'
              )
                li(style='margin-bottom: 8px') Every Friday you'll get an email asking about your wins for the week. Log them before the weekend so nothing gets lost.
                li(style='margin-bottom: 8px') Achievements are saved in STAR format — situation, task, action, result. Makes them easy to pull into a resume later.
                li(style='margin-bottom: 8px') You have 10 free achievements to get started. No credit card needed.

          tr
            td(style='padding: 30px 30px 0 30px')
              a(
                href=dashboardLink,
                style='background-color: #ff7a8a; color: #000000; text-decoration: none; padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 6px; display: inline-block; font-weight: bold'
              ) Go to your dashboard

          tr
            td(style='padding: 20px 30px 30px 30px')
              p(style='color: #333; font-size: 16px; margin: 24px 0 0 0') — Adrian, Career Fingerprint

  include footer.pug
